(Corrects to show he is CEO of NBAD in headline, first
paragraph.)  Michael Tomalin, chief executive
officer  National Bank of Abu Dhabi PJSC (NBAD) , said the search is
ongoing to find a new CEO and he’ll stay in the post for “as
long as it takes to find the right successor.”  Tomalin commented today at a press conference in Geneva.  To contact the reporter on this story:
